Virtual friends are not eyes 
who are watching us

give themselves.

Comment:
This looks like every other sci-fi/futuristic movie we've already seen - bits of Blade Runner, Minority Report, I Robot, Fifth Element, Judge Dredd etc etc.  

How they took something that had so many memorable visuals and remade it to look so generic, I have no idea.
